        <abstract> 
<p>Thanks for 5th edition of his book [<hi rend="italic">Natürliche</hi>] <hi rend="italic">Schöpfungsgeschichte</hi>.</p> 
            <p>CD continues with his experiments on the digestive power of plants, which is much like that of mammals.</p> 
<p>Is also preparing a revised edition of <hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>.</p> 
            <p>Would welcome hearing more of his ideas about Pangenesis.</p> 
<p>Postscript about <hi rend="italic">Anthropogenie</hi>, which has just arrived. EH’s astonishing productivity.</p> 
        </abstract>
